{
  "id": "62f701351ff461001d48f5f3",
  "title": "帰省",
  "created": 1660354872,
  "updated": 1683373089,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "62f701351ff461001d48f5f3",
      "text": "帰省",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354872,
      "updated": 1660354872
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70137e6003500009b4042",
      "text": "帰省(きせい)という言葉は（[hatori.icon]が調べた限りでは）[唐代]の[詩人][朱慶餘]の[漢詩]「送張景宣下第東歸」に由来する",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354872,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4043",
      "text": "[送張景宣下第東歸]（歸揚州覲省）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1666266474
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4044",
      "text": ">歸省值花時，閑吟落第詩。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4045",
      "text": ">高情憐道在，公論覺才遺。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4046",
      "text": ">春雨連淮暗，私船過馬遲。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4047",
      "text": ">離心可惆悵，爲有入城期。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4048",
      "text": "[https://zh.m.wikisource.org/zh/%E9%80%81%E5%BC%B5%E6%99%AF%E5%AE%A3%E4%B8%8B%E7%AC%AC%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%B8 送張景宣下第東歸 - 维基文库，自由的图书馆]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4049",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b404a",
      "text": "冒頭の「歸」は「帰」の[旧字体]であり、したがって歸省＝帰省である",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b404b",
      "text": "この詩は[全唐詩]巻514に載っているようだ（[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%85%A8%E5%94%90%E8%A9%A9 全唐詩 - Wikipedia]）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b404c",
      "text": "　[https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=en&chapter=369701 御定全唐詩 : 卷五百十四 - Chinese Text Project]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b404d",
      "text": "　[https://www.kanripo.org/text/KR4h0140/514?query=%E9%80%81%E5%BC%B5%E6%99%AF%E5%AE%A3%E4%B8%8B%E7%AC%AC%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%B8#514-6b Kanripo 漢籍リポジトリ : KR4h0140 御定全唐詩-清-聖祖玄燁]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b404e",
      "text": "日本語訳は誰かに任せた！[hatori.icon]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b404f",
      "text": "　機械翻訳ではあまりうまくいかない",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "645619665e90c00000e905bb",
      "text": "　全唐詩にあるなら江戸時代の文献から訓読を探せそう[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683364197,
      "updated": 1683364218
    },
    {
      "id": "645619845e90c00000e905bd",
      "text": "　　国立国会図書館デジタルコレクションあたりを頑張ればなんとか…",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683364227,
      "updated": 1683364251
    },
    {
      "id": "62f709f0b8bbfc000020cf70",
      "text": "学校で[漢文]習ったことあるしちょっとは読めるかなと思ったが一文字たりともわからんもんだ[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1660357105,
      "updated": 1660357161
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70a4eb8bbfc000020cf72",
      "text": "\t読み下せたとしても、詩を読み慣れてないと何が言いたいのかわからん感じの雰囲気がある",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1660357199,
      "updated": 1660357241
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70197e6003500009b4061",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354968,
      "updated": 1660354968
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70196e6003500009b4060",
      "text": "参考：[https://rnavi.ndl.go.jp/jp/guides/theme_asia_16.html 漢詩の出典｜リサーチ・ナビ｜国立国会図書館]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354966,
      "updated": 1660354966
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4050",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4051",
      "text": ">帰省の由来・語源",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4052",
      "text": ">唐代から見える漢語で、「帰」は「帰郷する」の意。「省」は「父母を顧みる」の意で使われる。つまり、「帰省」とは、本来は家を離れていた者が故郷に戻って、父母を顧みて大切にすること。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4053",
      "text": ">日本では江戸時代まではあまり使われなかったが、明治時代から現在と同じ意味で用いられるようになった。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4054",
      "text": "[http://yain.jp/i/%E5%B8%B0%E7%9C%81 帰省(きせい)とは - 由来・語源辞典]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4056",
      "text": "　省みる(かえりみる)ということで、帰省の「省」は反省・内省の「省」と同じ意味をもつようだ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354880
    },
    {
      "id": "64560bb8e5172d0000311f53",
      "text": "　父母を顧みるというより自分がのんびりするために帰省してる…[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1683360696,
      "updated": 1683360719
    },
    {
      "id": "64560bd5e5172d0000311f54",
      "text": "　 帰(不省)",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1683360725,
      "updated": 1683360741
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4057",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70426e6003500009b4063",
      "text": "最近では[新型コロナウイルス]感染拡大防止のために、[オンライン帰省]（実際に帰省する代わりに、[ビデオ通話]・[テレビ電話]により連絡を取ること）を推奨されることもある",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660355623,
      "updated": 1660355664
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70426e6003500009b4064",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660355623,
      "updated": 1660355623
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4059",
      "text": "類語：[帰郷]、[里帰り]、[藪入り]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660355031
    },
    {
      "id": "62f701d7e6003500009b4062",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660355031,
      "updated": 1660355031
    },
    {
      "id": "6456387f5e90c00000b1aaae",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/d3f4ce0148e192ff34f1c8d81c0241be][https://gyazo.com/73ccf09ef95863436894fec137f205cc]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683372160,
      "updated": 1683372163
    },
    {
      "id": "645638725e90c00000b1aaad",
      "text": " [礼記]や[令義解]にも「省」が引かれているらしい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683372146,
      "updated": 1683373072
    },
    {
      "id": "64563c1a5e90c000000c81b9",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683373083,
      "updated": 1683373083
    },
    {
      "id": "64563c1a5e90c000000c81ba",
      "text": " 大町桂月 (芳衛) , 佐伯常麿 著『誤用便覧 : 机上宝引』,文栄閣,明44.5. 国立国会図書館デジタルコレクション https://dl.ndl.go.jp/pid/862888 (参照 2023-05-06)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683373083,
      "updated": 1683373083
    },
    {
      "id": "64563c1c5e90c000000c81bb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683373085,
      "updated": 1683373085
    },
    {
      "id": "64563bd75e90c000000c81b3",
      "text": "礼記曲礼篇上",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683373016,
      "updated": 1683373089
    },
    {
      "id": "64563bd85e90c000000c81b4",
